  16 Oct 2015; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> tvheadend-4.0.6.ebuild:
  Fix usage of ffmpeg vs libav flags.

  ffmpeg flag means enable ffmpeg or libav. libav flags means use libav, lack
  of it use ffmpeg.

